en.name: TROY Squid Grips Small
en.description: TROY's patented, revolutionary rail insert is back available for Alpha Rails. Its composition of proprietary advanced rubber makes it heat resistant and extremely durable. The squid grips insert directly into the cooling holes, and may be cut to form any length or inserted end to end for longer lengths.

en.name: Troy Quick Attach Rail Section (2-Slot)
en.description: The Troy Quick Attach Rail Sections secures with two screws to a backer on the inside of certain Troy Rails. For use on Alpha, Delta, TRX 308, TRX Extreme, Troy HK rails and T-22 Sport Chassis, M7 Uppers and M7 Kit, the Troy Quick Attach Rail sections accommodate a full range of accessories and installing them solidly onto the rail.
